wikipedia_page.main: Luke Adam  Dean (born 14 May 1991) is an English professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Matlock Town.

response: Luke Dean (21 June 1913 – 1975) was an English footballer who played as a forward for Port Vale and Northwich Victoria.
Luke Dean is the name of:
*Luke Dean (footballer, born 1913), English professional footballer who played for Port Vale
*Luke Dean (footballer, born 1991), English professional footballer who plays for Harrogate Town
